      <title>特斯拉被勒令停止旧金山湾区工厂排放有毒排放</title>
      <link>https://apnews.com/article/tesla-toxic-emissions-san-francisco-bay-area-a1b3acb069200bc7a0a64623375c4938</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉必须解决其位于旧金山湾区的电动汽车制造工厂的空气质量问题。过去五年来，该工厂因涉嫌向大气排放有毒物质而累计违规超过 100 次。]]></description>
      <guid>https://apnews.com/article/tesla-toxic-emissions-san-francisco-bay-area-a1b3acb069200bc7a0a64623375c4938</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 00:19:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
